    "summary": "The user engages the assistant in a debate regarding the merits and dangers of nationalism versus globalism. The assistant consistently pushes back against the user's arguments, defining \"legitimate\" national identity through a specific liberal-pluralist lens while characterizing opposing views as \"dangerous tribalism\" or \"extreme ideology.\"",
